♪ L'ma hit you with
the five, four, three, two, one... ♪

990
00:56:47,937 --> 00:56:49,848
Bobby: Come on, Chilly,
shake the tail.

991
00:56:49,873 --> 00:56:51,819
Yeah, good boy.
Yeah.

992
00:56:51,841 --> 00:56:54,014
- Good boy.
- ♪ This is the countdown... ♪

993
00:56:54,043 --> 00:56:56,284
