997
00:57:01,818 --> 00:57:04,230
- Run, Chilly, run. Go!
- ♪ You know I won't let you down ♪

998
00:57:04,254 --> 00:57:05,995
♪ Let's keep going, another round ♪

999
00:57:06,022 --> 00:57:08,935
♪ L'ma hit you with
the five, four, three, two, one... ♪

1000
00:57:08,958 --> 00:57:11,905
See? You can do it, Chilly.

1001
00:57:15,965 --> 00:57:17,808
Good boy.
Go for it, Chilly.

1002
00:57:17,834 --> 00:57:21,611
Yeah. Good boy.
Yes! Go, Chilly!

1003
00:57:21,638 --> 00:57:24,175
Whoo!
He did it, you guys.

1004
00:57:33,483 --> 00:57:36,020
- Kizzy: That's disgusting.
- ♪ Five, four, three, two, one... ♪

1005
00:57:36,052 --> 00:57:37,725
- Bobby: Come on, Chilly.
- ♪ Want to see what I can do ♪

1006
00:57:37,754 --> 00:57:39,324
♪ You just gotta ask... ♪

1007
00:57:39,355 --> 00:57:41,733
Come on, one after the other.
You're doing it, Chilly.

