You're doing it.
You're doing it.

1010
00:57:47,030 --> 00:57:48,703
Yeah. Good job.

1011
00:57:48,731 --> 00:57:50,335
- Good. Good.
- ♪ My fears have gone away ♪

1012
00:57:50,366 --> 00:57:53,040
♪ It's time to fly ♪

1013
00:57:53,069 --> 00:57:54,412
♪ Can you move it?
Can you groove it? ♪

1014
